OL,3,CAfghans 'anxious' for result of
OL,4,Cinquiry into alleged special forces
OL,5,Cmurders
OL,7,FDr Nooralhaq Nasimi told ITV News
OL,8,Ffamilies in Afghanistan welcome the
OL,9,Finquiry
OL,11,FAfghan families are "anxious" about
OL,12,Fthe outcome of an inquiry into an
OL,13,Falleged cover-up of special forces
OL,14,Fkillings in Afghanistan, the director
OL,15,Fof the UK's Afghanistan and Central
OL,16,FAsian Association has said.
