OL,3,CAfghans 'anxious' for result of
OL,4,Cinquiry into alleged special forces
OL,5,Cmurders
OL,7,FDr Nooralhaq Nasimi told ITV News that
OL,8,Fthe inquiry into allegations of
OL,9,Funlawful killings by SAS troops
OL,10,Fbetween 2010 and 2013 was a "great
OL,11,Fstep".
OL,13,F"We want to see that the inquiry will
OL,14,Fhave some kind of outcome to see why
OL,15,Fthis was happening, and how we can
OL,16,Fprevent it in the future and how we
OL,17,Fcan also contact the families who lost
OL,18,Ftheir families in Afghanistan," he
OL,19,Ftold ITV News.
