OL,3,CAfghans 'anxious' for result of
OL,4,Cinquiry into alleged special forces
OL,5,Cmurders
OL,7,F"They are very anxious and they want
OL,8,Fto see the result of the inquiry."
OL,10,FThe inquiry is examining whether a
OL,11,Fspecial forces unit, known to the
OL,12,Fprobe as UKSF1, had a policy of
OL,13,Fexecuting males of "fighting age" who
OL,14,Fposed no threat in Afghanistan.
OL,16,FFormer Defence Secretary Sir Ben
OL,17,FWallace gave evidence in the inquiry
OL,18,Fon Monday, and has denied he "lacked
OL,19,Fcuriosity" when previously responding
OL,20,Fto the allegations.
