OL,5,Cmurders
OL,7,FIt comes after emails published in The
OL,8,FSunday Times revealed that former
OL,9,FVeterans' Minister Johnny Mercer wrote
OL,10,Fto Wallace in August 2020 expressing
OL,11,Fserious concerns about the killings of
OL,12,F33 people in 11 night raids in the war-
OL,13,Ftorn nation in 2011.
OL,15,FMercer previously told the Afghanistan
OL,16,FInquiry he was "angry" with Wallace,
OL,17,Fas well as the director of special
OL,18,Fforces and the chief of the general
OL,19,Fstaff.
