OL,7,FHe claimed they had "not done the job
OL,8,Fthat was incumbent upon them with
OL,9,Ftheir rank and privileges in those
OL,10,Forganisations".
OL,12,FHitting back at Mercer's claims on
OL,13,FMonday, the former defence secretary
OL,14,Fdescribed the claims that he lacked
OL,15,Fcuriosity as "highly inaccurate",
OL,16,Fadding: "I was absolutely inquisitive."
