OL,4,Cinquiry into alleged special forces
OL,5,Cmurders
OL,7,FAfghan families have accused UK
OL,8,Fspecial forces of conducting a
OL,9,F"campaign of murder" against
OL,10,Fcivilians, while senior officers and
OL,11,Fpersonnel at the Ministry of Defence
OL,12,F"sought to prevent adequate
OL,13,Finvestigation".
OL,15,FNasimi told ITV News: "They want to
OL,16,Fsee whether the British armed forces
OL,17,Facted unlawfully. If they acted
OL,18,Funlawfully, there should be some legal
OL,19,Fmeasure against those individuals
OL,20,Fwhich caused serious casualties
OL,21,Fagainst the civilians in Afghanistan."
