OL,5,Cmurders
OL,7,F"The community are very anxious," he
OL,8,Fadded.
OL,10,F"They welcome this inquiry. They are
OL,11,Fvery happy to see the result of this
OL,12,Finquiry to make sure those civilians
OL,13,Fwill have some sort of compensation
OL,14,Ffrom the British government."
OL,16,FWhen questioned at the inquiry,
OL,17,FWallace said: "Not only did I seek to
OL,18,Fdig deeper, I also even sought to dig
OL,19,Finternationally whether or not the
OL,20,Fassurances I'd been given were
OL,21,Ftruthful.
