OL,7,F"Secondly, I established this
OL,8,Finquiry... so I was absolutely
OL,9,Finquisitive. I held the department to
OL,10,Faccount if I felt that they were not
OL,11,Fproducing what we had asked for.
OL,13,F"But I also had to reiterate that we
OL,14,Fhad to act on the evidence before us,
OL,15,Fand that I also have a duty to the men
OL,16,Fand women of the armed forces to make
OL,17,Fsure that their reputation is not
OL,18,Fdragged through the mud or indeed
OL,19,Flibelled or besmirched without
OL,20,Fevidence."
