OL,7,FWallace was also questioned on a
OL,8,Fmissive sent by director of judicial
OL,9,Fengagement policy Peter Ryan in 2019,
OL,10,Fwhich concluded that allegations of
OL,11,Fspecial forces murders were "broadly
OL,12,Faccurate".
OL,14,FMr Glasgow asked: "Is that the sort of
OL,15,Fsubmission that one needs to pay
OL,16,Fattention to, Sir Ben?"
